                                                                            <li>Encouraging mobility and independence or aiding passive exercises as appropriate</li>
                                                                            <li>Post-operative infection control and safety management</li>
                                                                            <li>Tackling the factors that increase the risk of heart disease, such as smoking, poor diet and little physical exercise, if appropriate.</li>
